OL,3,C'High' alert for air pollution issued
OL,4,Cas 'hottest day of the year' expected
OL,6,FA high air pollution alert has been
OL,7,Fissued for London as the capital
OL,8,Fprepares for what is expected to be
OL,9,Fthe hottest day of the year so far.
OL,11,FCity Hall issued the warning for
OL,12,FThursday after Imperial College London
OL,13,Fforecasters detected an increase in
OL,14,Fair pollution from mainland Europe.
OL,16,FLocal sources of pollution alongside
OL,17,Fsouthern winds contribute to the high
OL,18,Fpollution levels.
