OL,3,C'High' alert for air pollution issued
OL,4,Cas 'hottest day of the year' expected
OL,6,F"We are urging Londoners to look after
OL,7,Fthemselves in this pollution alert,
OL,8,Fstop their engines idling, and refrain
OL,9,Ffrom burning wood or garden waste `
OL,10,Fall of which contribute to high levels
OL,11,Fof pollution.
OL,13,F"This is particularly important in
OL,14,Forder to protect those who are most
OL,15,Fvulnerable as we continue working to
OL,16,Fbuild a safer and greener London for
OL,17,Fall."
